<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>- 来自“隐世”私房菜,只用“山泉水鲩鱼”- </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200917/16b2ff96fa7148d8aa0ac84536a9b5c3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 来自“隐世”几十年的私房菜馆 </p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这家店其实来源于一家<strong>只接待私人宾客</strong>，“隐世”几十年的<strong>私房菜馆——筱布乐</strong>，近年来才开始对外开放！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200917/226f70da08d147adbde9700c2949fb83.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200917/767c41c34f514c90bb935b70e8470911.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">新开设了一家<strong>专门做鱼的“佬渔餐馆”</strong>，许多老饕就跟随脚步寻味而来！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200917/5bed3abf6c6b496aac1b40ab40e04826.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">|||</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200917/b1af0a3b51a24f7fb6bcdab7683f7dc1.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自家水库养殖的“山泉水皖鱼” </p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">他们家就是以“山泉水鲩鱼”出名的，自家拥有<strong>天然无污染的猫爪水库</strong>，水库养殖的鱼，从源头把关质量打造健康，水库的<strong>水质是饮用水级别</strong>，养出来的鱼鳞片都<strong>微微泛金</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200917/d0c2f143e33b4f8282e740c3befbbd28.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200917/16b2ff96fa7148d8aa0ac84536a9b5c3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">鱼儿都是<strong>割草喂养的</strong>，水库的水温低，鲩鱼们条条都是运动健将，养出来的<strong>鱼肉质紧实清甜</strong>，没<strong>有一点泥腥味</strong>~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200917/835092724a8846978a8ccb9495be68a7.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200917/d4912b38c69c4d24bde4cc4e45e9b4e0.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200917/019f6be1ef2941c2b7d20f78ca5ed1f5.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>- “山泉水鲩鱼”，焖多久都超嫩 - </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200917/33bb9d63265b480cb5dea04ceebfac97.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 大锅焖鱼，焖足30分钟还超嫩 </p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">焖鱼是佬渔的一大招牌，之前私房菜馆里就有许多<strong>食客专门驱车</strong>前来吃他们家焖鱼！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200917/e1491f9b3a5b4bc0aaa1c94462e3a9d6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200917/b186c5911fff46d69f34be2f6a1773bf.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">他们家的焖鱼是用<strong>原条鱼骨熬制的汤焖的</strong>，一开盖子鲜香浓郁，由<strong>几十年经验的大师傅</strong>焖制半小时，鱼肉鲜嫩甘甜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200917/1cf376bd2532487f99eac3e92e31f42e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200917/43140d9e42184a7dac618a932ecbb5cc.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">鲩鱼的肉质非常好，就算是一直焖制着，<strong>鱼肉也不会变老</strong>，入口依旧<strong>鲜嫩，甜滑</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200917/2d010ff43f504041907bf49c8e3c2c58.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">焖鱼还可以按照自己的喜好添加配菜，<strong>强烈安利佛手瓜、芋头、白贝、罗氏虾</strong>！佛手瓜和芋头<strong>吸饱鲜美的汤汁</strong>，入口即化，吃完之后嘴里还会<strong>一直回甜</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200917/8bdf4fd5d54345068a9a530c21926afa.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鱼+羊 = 鱼羊鲜 </p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">焖鱼+羊肉=超鲜美的鱼羊鲜！在<strong>焖鱼里加上一份东山羊</strong>，在鱼肉鲜甜中又增添一丝羊肉香气，绝！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200917/e017cd3c3e8146499643f348a6f21a8b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">羊肉是已经焖制过的了，又在<strong>焖鱼煲里吸收了鲜美的鱼汤</strong>，肉质依旧弹爽，胶原蛋白满满！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200917/d6ba5ed5add94d76b88f94fe7717b64e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200917/0e6de7cf133048b89a61d24c5bd44855.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200917/d791a061ad36459391fdb1848197899b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>- 一鱼N吃，"爽、甜、鲜、滑" - </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200917/a3fec62e532e4e6dbc452adef7ad90be.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 招牌顺德鱼生，捞住吃 </p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">顺德人对鱼生的执着不亚于重庆人对火锅的执着，<strong>一条4-6斤的鲩鱼</strong>，在佬渔这里它是要被“片”成刺身的~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200917/7693ba24523040999740284ebafb3ae3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">师傅是有着20多年资历，手起刀落鱼就变成了一片片<strong>晶莹剔透的鱼生</strong>，厚薄适中，看起来跟果冻似的！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200917/7ed54330cde8411fb9a0ad4b34fd7e7e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">夹起一片晶莹剔透的鱼生，再配上顺德鱼生N件套，一齐捞个风生水起！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200917/6415a786f0d649a0b03d8e824db4a521.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200917/88492736bf5941aab6e1756c8412644c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200917/e8870dcb203442e3943f3ed822126322.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200917/35fbad1c20ad436bab423946a2d49bb6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">入口先是配料的香浓，在后面就是鲩鱼生的<strong>鲜！甜！爽！</strong>口感清爽不黏口，<strong>一点泥腥味都没有</strong>，越嚼越甜！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200917/bfcb390f98a043afbb3643150c200556.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200917/bc74b6689f564307979ca39c23fb5dad.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">厚薄相同的鲩鱼生，新鲜的程度仿佛在你的嘴里跳舞，<strong>鱼脂香，肉质甜</strong>，这盘鱼生，我给满分💯！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200917/0af65da73ee244d693d5f8ad78d13ae7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 一鱼N吃，焖炒煎蒸炸都得 </p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">鱼皮除了凉拌，还能这么做！将<strong>鲜虾滑酿在鲩鱼皮上</strong>，香煎至熟，入口香脆，还能嚼到虾肉粒！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200917/181e94f1bfab4a69a28a8b98260fa0bc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200917/adebaf1cf1b8406d823a846aadc2520e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200917/7da1eb8555c74d148445a9385ac53c3f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">开了一条鱼，还有鱼骨那些，<strong>只要加18</strong>，就可以多一味菜！1鱼N吃，焖炒煎蒸炸都得！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200917/aa2910a4240343fe99425826e31a964d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200917/e6ca96abc54c4123b164f808611f0680.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200917/51ef07e914b1472abe45dc0fdea69a44.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>- 专门吃“山泉水鲩鱼”的粤菜馆 - </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">佬渔是一家专门吃“山泉水鲩鱼”的餐厅，足足有800㎡，自带鱼池！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200917/5a204093234c417abf795c55ee378a9b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200917/6ecf8f547b7e483582876587ab7be591.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">店里是以天蓝色为主调，明亮大方，用餐环境宽敞舒适，还有私密包间，十分合适家庭朋友聚餐！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200917/48af9a3ac7ba4b20aafa6b55703cc15d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200917/ef78b62659354476a2ff1c05d4f23e29.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>🐟佬渔餐馆 🐟</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>到d按tips，即可享受</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> ①原58的虾胶煎酿鱼皮free送 </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200917/ec646e24869f40fb8ea451cc9556920d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
